{
  "stem": "27335.3",
  "chunk_idx": 1,
  "model": "openai/gpt-oss-120b",
  "elapsed_s": 9.0,
  "sentences_input": [
    {
      "segment_idx": 1,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "So turned around, and there is this fellow I already knew.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 1,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "He was introduced on Sunday.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 1,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "He was driving a-- a-- a-- a bread truck as a-- a delivery-- he said, Andy, Andy, you know what's the news?",
      "word_count": 22
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 1,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 7,
      "text": "Very excitingly and so.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 1,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 8,
      "text": "What?",
      "word_count": 1
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 1,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 9,
      "text": "What?",
      "word_count": 1
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 1,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 10,
      "text": "What's the news?",
      "word_count": 3
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 1,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 11,
      "text": "He said, the war broke out.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 1,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 12,
      "text": "He said, Germany invaded Poland.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 1,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 13,
      "text": "And it was-- it was September the 1st already.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 1,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 14,
      "text": "And-- but he had a radio, and he was-- he was up at 3 o'clock to deliver bread to the house, you know?",
      "word_count": 23
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 1,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 15,
      "text": "So he-- he had-- he had [? affair ?] news.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 1,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 16,
      "text": "It-- it was really a shock.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 1,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 17,
      "text": "And then on the double, hurry, on the double I ran down to the-- to Wellington Street from Dundas and-- Dundas.",
      "word_count": 21
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 1,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 18,
      "text": "And-- and that's my area and told people there.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 1,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 19,
      "text": "Some there went in the early [INAUDIBLE].",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 1,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 20,
      "text": "And they didn't hear it when I told them.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 1,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 21,
      "text": "Well, they smiled.",
      "word_count": 3
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 1,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 22,
      "text": "They thought I am making a joke.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 1,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 23,
      "text": "But didn't take really very long, only 10, 15 minutes.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 1,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 24,
      "text": "They all knew.",
      "word_count": 3
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 1,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 25,
      "text": "And then it was a shock.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 1,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 26,
      "text": "Well, what to do now?",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 1,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 27,
      "text": "We knew.",
      "word_count": 2
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 1,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 28,
      "text": "We knew.",
      "word_count": 2
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 2,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "There's a war.",
      "word_count": 3
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 2,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "There's a war time on.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 2,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "That-- the leftist movement will be under-- under pressure.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 2,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "And so-- and sure enough, sure enough, by October came-- came a order in council in Ottawa, part of the-- the government.",
      "word_count": 22
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 2,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "First the Communist Party and all these leftist organizations were outlawed.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 3,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "But-- but two [PAUSES FOR 5 SECONDS] [INAUDIBLE] organization was spared, because it was a government-chartered organization.",
      "word_count": 17
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 3,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "But the cultural organization was banned.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 3,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "But all paper, all paper were spared because the RCMP went around, you see, to all the-- they had the [INAUDIBLE].",
      "word_count": 21
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 3,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "And they-- they didn't come to us, to our paper and the Wochenblatt.",
      "word_count": 13
    }
  ],
